      • filter

        public static List<String> filter(String pattern,
                                  List<String> list)
            
        filter list of string with regex
        list = ["dog cat", "big pig"]
        regex = "pig"
        filter(regex, list) => ["dog", "cat"]

        regex is created from Pattern.compile(pattern);
    
    
        Note: if pattern = "" => return List<String> list = new ArrayList<String>();
        ------------------------------------------------------------------   
        // remove all comments from Haskell file
        String pattern = "^\\s*--";
        List<String> list = Arrays.asList("code 1", "code 2", " -- Haskell comment");
        List<String> flist = filter(pattern, list);
        Print.printList(flist);
